\"BC\", MessageDigest.getInstance(\"SHA-256\", provider).getProvider().getName());\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void loadClassUsesLibraryClassLoaderForAlgorithmMappingClass() {\n        Class<?> loadedClass = ClassUtil.loadClass(BouncyCastleProvider.class, AES_MAPPINGS_CLASS);\n\n        assertNotNull(loadedClass);\n        assertEquals(AES_MAPPINGS_CLASS, loadedClass.getName());\n    }\n}\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 534, "output": 1993, "cacheRead": 43520, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 46047, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780909789735, "responseId": "resp_01a67ab516ed9015016a2686de4b5081969685a9036d97b515"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_15TP2xcrp5l4umc0baTBEVjs|fc_01a67ab516ed9015016a268705470881969a708fea14ee3b5b", "toolName": "edit", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/ClassUtilTest.java."}], "details": {"diff": "    ...\n  6  */\n  7 package org_bouncycastle.bcprov_jdk15to18;\n  8 \n  9 import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;\n+10 import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertNotNull;\n 10 import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertTrue;\n 11 \n 12 import java.security.MessageDigest;\n 13 \n+15 import org.bouncycastle.jcajce.provider.symmetric.util.ClassUtil;\n 14 import org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.BouncyCastleProvider;\n 15 import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n 16 \n 17 public class ClassUtilTest {\n+20     private static final String AES_MAPPINGS_CLASS = \"org.bouncycastle.jcajce.provider.symmetric.AES$Mappings\";\n+21 \n 18     @Test\n 19     void providerConstructionLoadsAlgorithmMappingsThroughClassUtil() throws Exception {\n 20         BouncyCastleProvider provider = new BouncyCastleProvider();\n 21 \